  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下页面发布的完整生命周期，从草稿到正式发布。我觉得可以分成三个阶段：草稿阶段、调度阶段和已发布阶段。每个阶段都有关键的状态标记和操作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Drafting",
        "Scheduling",
        "Published"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，三个阶段。草稿阶段的核心是什么？是创建页面本身，还是内容块的添加？我需要确认这两个的先后顺序。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Create page",
        "Add content blocks"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "创建页面先发生，这时候published_at是空的，我们内部用Logistics_StockLevel来标记这个状态。然后编辑才会通过content_page_blocks去添加具体内容块。这两个动作都属于草稿阶段。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Create page",
        "published_at is nil",
        "Logistics_StockLevel",
        "content_page_blocks"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，草稿阶段已经画好了。接下来是调度阶段——这里的关键动作是设置发布时间吧？还有其他的配置更新吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Scheduling",
        "Set published_at"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，调度阶段的核心是设定published_at为当前时间或未来时间，这时候页面进入scheduled状态。同时运营人员可能会更新隐私设置、布局或者slug，这些改动会触发updated_at的缓存键更新。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Set published_at",
        "scheduled",
        "Update privacy/layout/slug",
        "cached keys",
        "updated_at"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "最后到已发布阶段，判断条件是published_at小于等于当前时间？还有可见性逻辑需要体现吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Published",
        "published_at <= now",
        "Visible"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，published_at <= now就代表已发布。可见性方面要说明：页面实际显示需要policy允许，要么是公开隐私设置，要么用户有授权。这个权限检查很重要。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "published_at <= now",
        "published",
        "Visible if policy allows",
        "privacy public",
        "authorized"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。整个时间线从草稿创建、内容填充，到调度设置发布时间，最后满足条件后发布并受权限控制可见。三个阶段的关键状态和流转都清晰了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Page Publish Lifecycle",
        "Drafting",
        "Scheduling",
        "Published"
      ],
